    "## Overview\n",
    "\n",
    "Cutting the cord, the action of being rid of the old standardized subscriptions of bundled cable television has seen an explosion over the last few years. This action allows the consumer the freedom to choose programs you want to watch at cheaper alternatives. Consequently, the alternatives presented are streaming services such as Netflix, Amazon Prime Video, HBO Max, YouTube TV, Hulu and many more. Kenneth Research, a leading market research agency, projects the growth of the global streaming platform market to [increase by 21% over the next decade](<https://www.globenewswire.com/en/news-release/2022/10/17/2535260/0/en/Global-Video-Streaming-Market-is-Projected-to-Grow-at-a-CAGR-of-21-During-2022-2031-Rising-Adoption-of-Digital-Media-to-Elevate-Growth-Kenneth-Research.html>).\n",
    "\n",
    "An exploratory report analysis for the content streaming platforms; Netflix, Amazon Prime Video, Hulu and Disney Plus as of mid-2021 includes the following factors:\n",
    "-\tContent Maturity Ratings\n",
    "-\tLibrary Catalog "
