    "## Content Library by Age\n",
    "\n",
    "**Netflix**\n",
    "\n",
    "A high percentage of Netflix's library was initially released in the years 2018, 2017, and 2019, each holding over a thousand titles individually. Netflix's library reveals a sparse collection of released content prior to the 2000s. The oldest content available on the streaming platform, Pioneers: First Women Filmmakers, is a TV Show collection. The collection restores films from women who tackled hot-button issues, transcended norms, and left a mark on the history of cinema and the industry."
