    "**Disney+**\n",
    "\n",
    "Disney boasts the largest collection of older content. Which is likely attributed to housing their Walt Disney Studio Films on the streaming service.Their animation studio has [produced 61 films, launching in 1937](<https://www.disneyanimation.com/life-at-disney/>) and producing classic films such as Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs, Pinocchio, Dumbo and Bambi\n",
